## Troubleshooting

### Stream Not Created
Check NATS pod logs for init script errors:
```bash
kubectl logs -n recon deployment/nats
```

### Messages Not Delivered
1. Verify stream exists: `nats stream info {STREAM}`
2. Check consumer: `nats consumer info {STREAM} {CONSUMER}`
3. Verify subject pattern matches

### Connection Refused
1. Check NATS pod status: `kubectl get pods -n recon -l app=nats`
2. Verify service: `kubectl get svc -n recon nats`
3. Check network policies allow connection

